ery in Bolivar Roads when we stop to bunker. Not ideal, but unavoidable if loading in Beaumont. Otherwise, port costs were in line with the generation aside from the additional port\u0027s costs which are covered in freight at $63k. We had 10.5 days on demurrage at a rate of $34,000, contributing to the PnL. Additional bunkers were consumed in port due to the additional port, while laden bunkers were reduced due to the half day reduction in passage when disport was changed from Pajaritos to Tuxpan."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-08-02T12:15:16.91","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Tuxpan Port costs less than PDA"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-07-18T13:51:28.637","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Due to supplier availability after the hurricane, FW had to be delivered in Galveston Anchorage"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-07-12T20:08:55.65","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Updated demurrage"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-07-09T15:15:12.19","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Bolivar Roads required a pilot for bunkering/FW"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-07-08T13:00:15.17","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Only one berth at Tampico, vsl departed sooner than expected."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-07-03T20:24:52.707","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Extended time and additional berth CM"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-06-28T16:52:52.137","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Additional time expected in Tampico. Updated Demurrage."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-06-26T13:23:36.31","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Bolivar Roads pilotage for bunkering higher than estimated. Also had FW delivery as BMT does not allow barges alongside."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-06-26T13:09:57.403","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Tampico included as disport."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-06-21T15:51:20.733","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"vessel ultimately departed BMT 21 eam... 4 days demurrage estimate added for Tuxpan basis agent expectations"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-06-20T12:40:16.553","